  Dâavoir voulu changer de place.â

Beauty says of herself, in the piece of that name:

  âJe hais le mouvement qui dÃ©place les lignes;
  Et jamais je ne pleure et jamais je ne ris.â

He abhors the natural as much as he loves the artificial. Thus he
