âI am light ... but this is my loneliness, that I am engirdled with
light.... I live in my own light; I drink back into myself the flames
that break forth from me.â

âMute over the roaring sea art thou this day arisen for me.â âThey
divine nothing from the roaring of my happiness.â âSing, and riot in
