into thy chariot, Storm!... Like a cry and a huzza would I glide away
over vast seas.â âEruptive insanity forever hovers above humanity as
its greatest danger.â (He is, of course, thinking of himself when
speaking of âhumanity.â) âIn these days it sometimes happens that a
gentle, temperate, self-contained man becomes suddenly frenzied, breaks
